OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry and
OL,6,Ffine end to the day with plenty of
OL,7,Fevening sunshine. Staying dry
OL,8,Fovernight with clear spells, some
OL,9,Fpatchy low cloud in northern parts and
OL,10,Flight winds. A cool night for many
OL,11,Fparticularly in rural areas.
OL,12,
OL,13,CMonday:FBlue skies at first, before
OL,14,Fcloud builds a little into the
OL,15,Fafternoon. Low cloud may linger around
OL,16,Fsome coasts in the north. Warm in the
OL,17,Fsunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
